WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.630 --> 00:00:04.000
Javobingiz uchun rahmat, bu yerda hech qanaqangi 
to‘g‘ri yoki noto‘g‘ri javob yo‘q.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.040
Demak, keling, siz qilishingiz mumkin bo‘lgan 
bir nechta kuzatuvlar haqida gaplashamiz.

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:11.670
Avvalo, siz kodning boshlanishi va 
oxirida keladigan g‘alati burchakli 

00:00:11.670 --> 00:00:12.485
qavslarni ko‘rgan bo‘lishingiz mumkin.

00:00:12.485 --> 00:00:15.215
Yana mana bu g‘alati yotiq chiziqni ham.

00:00:15.215 --> 00:00:18.035
Lekin bu faqatgina tugashida 
ishlatiladi, boshida emas.

00:00:18.035 --> 00:00:19.665
Bu yerda oldinroq tanishib 
chiqqanligimiz tufayli 

00:00:19.665 --> 00:00:22.085
biz biladigan TextView so‘zi yozilgan.

00:00:23.475 --> 00:00:26.505
Va u katta T va V harflari bilan 

00:00:26.505 --> 00:00:28.160
 camel case formatida ko‘rsatilgan.

00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:30.360
Endi siz android haqida nimadir 
ko‘rishingiz mumkin: matn.

00:00:30.360 --> 00:00:34.060
Va bu yerdagi ikki nuqta va undan 
keyin keladigan tenglik kabi 

00:00:34.060 --> 00:00:35.720
tinish belgilari biroz 
g‘alati tuyulishi mumkin.

00:00:35.720 --> 00:00:37.950
Endi Happy Birthday deb 
yozilgan qismni ko‘ramiz.

00:00:37.950 --> 00:00:40.440
Bu esa xuddi biz telefonda 
ko‘radiganimizdek qilib ko‘rsatilgan.

00:00:40.440 --> 00:00:42.690
Demak, ular qandaydir 
bog‘langan bo‘lishi mumkin.

00:00:42.690 --> 00:00:45.197
Shunday qilib bu ham 
bir kuzatuv bo‘la oladi.

00:00:45.197 --> 00:00:50.338
Undan keyin orqa fonining rangi to‘qroq, 
kulrang bo‘lgan narsaga e’tibor qaratamiz.

00:00:50.338 --> 00:00:53.339
Shuningdek TextView 
kulrang fonga egaligi ham 

00:00:53.339 --> 00:00:55.070
bu bilan bog‘liq bo‘la oladi.

